            "title": "日股半日升約3.1%　重上5萬點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日股連跌4日後顯著反彈，日經指數重上5萬點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">指數半日收報50025點，升1487點，升幅3.06%。</p>\n</div>",
